===== Condition =====

while true do
  ...
end

-- try this
x = 1
while x <= 3 do
  print(x);
  x = x + 1;
end

-- comment
initial x = 1
while x <= 3 then print x value
x = x + 1 (x = 1 + 1) now x = 2
x still <= 3 then print x value
x = x + 1 (x = 2 + 1) now x = 3
x still <= 3 then print x value
x = x + 1 (x = 3 + 1) now x = 4
now x is out of range. end loop.
